Interface Compliance.CheckInvocation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Invocable<ComplianceTypes.Info>
    Enclosing interface:
    Compliance

    public static interface Compliance.CheckInvocation
extends com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Invocable<ComplianceTypes.Info>
    Invocable that represents the Compliance#check vAPI operation.
    To execute the operation call Invocable.invoke() or Invocable.invoke(com.vmware.vapi.bindings.client.InvocationConfig).

    • Method Detail

      • checkSpec

        Compliance.CheckInvocation checkSpec(ComplianceTypes.CheckSpec checkSpec)
        Sets optional check operation parameter. Can be null.
        Parameters:
        checkSpec - Parameter specifies the entities on which storage policy compliance check is to be invoked. The storage compliance Info ComplianceTypes.Info is returned. If null, the behavior is equivalent to a ComplianceTypes.CheckSpec with CheckSpec#vmHome set to true and CheckSpec#disks populated with all disks attached to the virtual machine.
